          {
            "fontSize": "20px",
            "fontWeight": 400,
            "lineHeight": 2,
          }
        }
      >
        What is Refugee Flow?
      </p>
      <p
        animate={false}
        className="sc-gsFSXt kzZNSy"
        isClosed={true}
      >
        Refugee Flow is an interactive visualization that brings together conflict data, migration routes, and asylum statistics to help users understand the global displacement crisis. It combines multiple authoritative datasets into one explorable experience.
